Oprah, by the way, never even moved into the place.

These are two sharp blows to the media savvy businesswoman, ones that followed the mightiest of blows: when her much anticipated OWN Network hit airwaves to disappointing numbers.

But since the network’s dark first days, things have begun to look up and Oprah may yet redeem her juggernaut status among TV types.

